Rating: 4
I tried this recipe yesterday and it turned out fantastic! I read the other reviews and opted to use the hard boiled egg yolk. I made sure that I mashed it really fine. I also added the 1/2 tsp of salt suggested by onther reviewer and then went one baby step further and added about 1/2 to 3/4 tsp of vanilla to the mix. The shortcakes turned out light yellow on the inside with a sugar cookie like taste and an biscuit (very short and light) consistency. A real hit: will use this again.

